article_id:1907,category_name:News,title_name:Gala Dragalia Remix Is Now Live!,image_path:,message:<div>Gala Dragalia Remix started at <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1610604000"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div>What are Gala Dragalia and Gala Dragalia Remix?</div><div>The initial appearance rate for 5★ adventurers and dragons is boosted to 6%, which is up from the standard 4%! If you get a 5★ summon or 5★ featured summon, the appearance rate will return to the initial 6%.</div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);">・The newly-added 5★ adventurers Kimono Elisanne (flame) and Kimono Luca (wind) will also appear in the next summon showcase.</span></div><div><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);">・Adventurers added in past Gala Dragalia summon showcases may appear in this summon showcase as well. For information about which adventurers may appear, tap Summon on the in-game footer menu, then select Appearance Rates and check the Appearance Rates section.</span></div><div><br></div><div>Newly added featured adventurers:</div><div>5★ Kimono Elisanne (flame/lance)</div><div>5★ Kimono Luca (wind/axe)</div><div><br></div><div>Featured adventurer from past Gala Dragalia summon showcases:</div><div>5★ Gala Mym (flame/lance)</div><div><br></div><div>Gala Dragalia Remix appearance rates:</div><div>5★ total: 6.00%</div><div>5★ featured total: 1.50% (Adventurers: 1.50%)</div><div>5★ standard total: 4.50% (Adventurers: 1.50%, Dragons: 3.00%)</div><div>4★ standard total: 16.00% (Adventurers: 8.55%, Dragons: 7.45%)</div><div>3★ standard total: 78.00% (Adventurers: 47.00%, Dragons: 31.00%)</div><div><br></div><div>Gala Dragalia Remix event duration:</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1610604000"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1610949599"></span></div><div><br></div><div>Get a closer look at the featured adventurers below.</div><div><br></div><div>Featured adventurers:</div><div>
