ther information, please see the following notification.</div><div><a href="https://dragalialost.com/en/news/detail/1914">https://dragalialost.com/en/news/detail/1914</a></div><div><br></div><div>For more information about summoning, tap Summon on the in-game footer menu, then select Showcase Info and check the Details tab.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1610604000,update_time1610516112